org.openjdk.jol.datamodel

接口 DataModel

  • 所有已知实现类:
    Model32, Model64, Model64_CCPS, Model64_COOPS_CCPS, ModelVM

    public interface DataModel
    Describes the data model, notably, the basic types sizes.
    作者:
    Aleksey Shipilev
